### Generate a Barplot
plt.figure(figsize=(18,9))
plot = sns.barplot(top_6['total_deaths'], top_6['Country'])
for i,(value,name) in enumerate(zip(top_6['total_deaths'],top_6['Country'])):
    plot.text(value,i-0.05,f'{value:,.0f}',size=10)
plt.show()
